               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Mǝʿrāf, The Common of the Office (fols. 3ra-59vb) 
 I-1) Wāzemā,
                     The Office of Vigils (fols. 3ra-12vb)
 I-2) Kǝśtat za-ʾaryām, The festive
                     Office (fols. 12vb-24ra
 I-3) Sǝbḥāta nagh, The Office of Matins (fols.
                     24ra-50vb), incomplete
 I-4) Śǝrʿāta ʾaddäraräs, The order of celebrating
                     the Office (fols. 51ra-53vb)
 I-5) Sacerdotal prayers (fols.
                     55ra-59vb)
 - Liṭon (fols. 55ra-58ra)
 - Za-yǝnaggǝś za-Yāred (fols.
                     58ra-59vb), incomplete
 
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
